					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"スス子", "Susuko"},
					"“I thought the Pervert Order praised the original god of perversion, Skeetus?”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"スス子", "丝丝子"},
					"“但是变态性教原本不就是在赞扬变态之神赛克罗斯吗？”",
